    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a bit heartbroken to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to experience the joy of driving a truly pristine machine. This car has been my absolute pride and joy, kept tucked away in a climate-controlled garage and pampered with the best care possible. It looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014honestly, you\u2019d be hard-pressed to find a single blemish. It\u2019s a real head-turner that deserves a home where it\u2019ll be just as loved as it was here. Come by for a coffee and a look, you won't be disappointed!",
