    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an echelon-tier specimen for the true petrolhead. This unit features a blueprint-balanced rotating assembly with forged internals, ensuring surgical compression ratios and a perfectly linear power band. The drivetrain is absolute\u2014zero lash in the differential and a transmission that snaps through the gates with recalibrated synchros and a short-throw linkage. We\u2019ve optimized the thermal management system with a high-flow aluminum core to ensure peak operating temps even under heavy load. The chassis rigidity is factory-spec, free from any harmonic resonance or subframe fatigue. This is a turn-key masterpiece of mechanical synergy, meticulously curated for those who demand engineering excellence over mere aesthetics. No parasitic draws, no vacuum leaks, just pure, unadulterated performance.",
      "price": 44800.0,
